{"tid":2289802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日澳元首簽署防衛協議加強應對中國軍事擴張","createTime":"2020-11-17T13:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T23:06:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6cdd7ac735bb834f2ca4cbe54a93a0ca65d98afd","tid":2289802,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"日澳元首簽署防衛協議加強應對中國<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫理森訪問東京，與日本首相菅義偉會談，雙方簽署防衛協議，加強應對中國。協議包括容許兩國軍隊互訪，並進行聯合訓練。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉在會後記者會指，日本和澳洲在安全和防衛方面的合作，對印太地區和平穩定日益重要，指今次與澳洲達成協議，將兩國軍事合作提升到新水平。莫理森就指，和日本的特殊戰略夥伴關係將會變得更加牢固，形容是兩國防衛合作上的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n日澳就防衛協議已經進行6年談判，是日本除了美軍外，首次容許別國軍隊進入領土。分析認為，日澳加強合作是為了應對中國在區內的日益增強的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2366706&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=8b0e8d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366706</a>"},{"pid":"19783f393136a9eef4eca9f5a924f6bb667ec07e","tid":2289802,"uid":159583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"嗰頭先簽完rcep"},{"pid":"574c90da177a2629db3f9812d66047c3f553a0be","tid":2289802,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03d0395a0482d19cb1d1fa819cf7fdd2df6a047","tid":2289802,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19783f393136a9eef4eca9f5a924f6bb667ec07e","tid":2289802,"uid":159583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"嗰頭先簽完rcep"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"又傾又砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d3d5b5e7a0283e407fa30f93156aa0